name: RARE VISITOR! SMOKY Ukraine Air Alliance Antonov An-12 at Calgary Airport
description:
A super interesting visitor to end the year! This Ukraine Air Alliance Antonov An-12 paid a daylight visit to Calgary International Airport just a few days before Christmas, seen here arriving on 35L and taxiing into customs, and then departing 35R a few hours later in some immaculate golden hour lighting.
